4 bb b--black" target="_blank">The Beguiling</a> (also the last place I saw live music before COVID). My sentimentality aside, the video also notably features Montreal&#39;s James Goddard, aka <a href="https://skin0tone.bandcamp.com/" class="black no-underline fw4 bb b--black" target="_blank">Skin Tone</a>, materializing as a semi-transparent spectre mid-set to lend a little ghost sax to the festivities.</p><p class='maxread center'>GHOST SAX.</p><p class='maxread center'>See you in 2021, newsletter people. Stay safe.</p><div class='wide-media media'><div class='overflow-hidden aspect-ratio aspect-ratio--16x9'><!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/loose.dtd">
